  "text": "Let us notice that in [CITATION_1] the authors encountered a similar problem for related but different reasons. Their non-interference Property 1 recalled Sec. 2 is used in a case similar to the architectural case illustrated by Fig. 5(c) because the both controllers \"import\" the shared machine, hence can interfere with each another.",
